reviewText: Toddler must have, if they like garbage trucks anyways. Pretty cheesy and kinda hokey- but it beats the endless cycle of peppa. Wish it was longer, but like it overall. I think for the price it's a solid buy.
My son LOVES this movie. It's great, and both my son and daughter watch it over and over again. It's educational, too, teaching shapes and whatnot. Thanks!
